body.description: Give your body what it wants, all in one convenient bottle, with Centrum MultiGummies Multi+ Omega 3 Adult Multivitamin. Each multivitamin gummy is formulated with 11 nutrients to support overall wellness—including B-Vitamins, vitamin D and antioxidants (7). Centrum Multi+ Omega 3 multivitamin supports heart health (1)(2), normal brain function (3), eye health (4), daily energy needs (5) and normal immune function (6)(7). Each of these Centrum multivitamin gummies also contains an added boost of omega-3 fatty acid, with 7 mg EPA and 33 mg DHA. These multivitamin gummies are gluten-free with no artificial flavors or sweeteners. First purchase is good, however the second purchase the gummies stick to each others.
